My interpretation (SPOILERS); 

The raven can in fact speak; because the raven is YOU. As you travel through you gather items. These are conversations that the people of the town have given you, but when you go back they have nothing else to discuss. Thus the raven is sad because he realises that nobody truely accepted him. He is an outcast and the townsfolk only wanted to talk about their life.

